&lt;p&gt;HULK. We made a world. I was the Green King. And Caiera the Oldstrong was my
queen. But your &amp;ldquo;heroes&amp;rdquo; sent a bomb. Killed a million people. Now this
city will fall. You have twenty-four hours to evacuate. &lt;br/&gt; &lt;span class="citation-ref"&gt;&lt;a href="#WorldWarHulk-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Alien (2021 - 2023)</title><link>https://www.curiosities.dev/fiction/alien-2021-2023/</link><pubDate>Sat, 07 Oct 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.curiosities.dev/fiction/alien-2021-2023/</guid><description>&lt;style&gt;
